data.description: This fantastic Fishers home has so much space! Over 3,500sqft to spread out in. Main floor has a separate office, living room, great room, and then on to the kitchen. Granite counters, island, walk in pantry all flow to an oversized eating area. Whether for coffee or full meals, this space fits the bill. Upstairs is an amazing loft, big enough for couches and TV. The 4 bedrooms are all oversized, especially the master. Speaking of the master bedroom, it has dual vanities (separated by a wall for marital bliss) huge closets and plenty more storage. Outside the back yard is fenced and ready for action. And the garage has plenty of extra storage space, and still room for 2 cars! All this with a beautiful brick front and awesome corner lot, this is the home for you.
